Scripts in this directory are generated by puppet
formanaging the voms-admin service.

Scripts:

** voms-admin-install-<vo>.sh   
This script does not touch the database. It just sets up the voms-admin application.
It is currently executed by puppet automatically as required.


** voms-admin-create-<vo>.sh
This connects to datbaase and creates a fresh schema for a fresh VO.
It is NOT currently ran by puppet ever.

** voms-admin-update-<vo>.sh
This connects to a database and updates an existing schema for a VO.
It is NOT currently ran by puppet ever.

** voms-admin-destroy-<vo>.sh
This connects to a database and destroys an existing schema for a VO.
It is NOT currently ran by puppet ever.


